                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290910-218-off1203 t18290910-218-cd1204"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 1s.; 1 gold pin, value 7s.; two rows of beads, value 2s.; 1 silver stopper, value 2s.; 1 pair of ear-rings. value 2s.; 2 pockets, value 2s., and 20 half-crowns, the property of Marry Allen, <rs id="t18290910-218-viclabel1205" type="occupation">widow</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290910-218-victim2000 t18290910-218-viclabel1205"></join>; and 1 bonnet, value 25s., the goods of 
                     
