                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290910-218-off1203 t18290910-218-crimeloc1206"></join>; she has not been in my house, to my knowledge, for sixteen or seventeen months - I do not know who took these things, but I missed them on Monday, the 27th of July.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18290910-218-person2001">
                  MATILDA 
                  JONES
               <interp inst="t18290910-218-person2001" type="surname" value="JONES"></interp>
